title: FoxTrot - 1996 through 2014 {WebComixFan}
description:
"FOXTROT" Web Comic

"FoxTrot" (gocomics.com/foxtrot) by Bill Amend really needs no introduction.  It's been running in newspapers worldwide since 1988.  It revolves around the daily lives of the Fox family, parents Andrea and Roger and their children, Peter, Paige and Jason.  The strip covers a wide range of subject matter, including spoofs of pop culture fads, nerd culture, and popular consumer products.  "FoxTrot" began appearing online as well as in newspapers in 1996.  In 2007, the strip dropped from daily publication to a Sunday-only schedule.

This torrent collects the "FoxTrot" comics from 1996 to 2014 in a set of CBR files, one for each year
